front.title: •Kir Kanos (V)
front.gametext: When deployed, may take a Royal Guard into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. During battle, if with an Imperial and present at a site, once per game may cancel a non-[Immune to Sense] Interrupt.
front.lore: Fiercely devoted Royal Guard. Feels deeply indebted to those who risk their life for him. Unaware of the extent of Palpatine's atrocities and cruelty.
